<!-- Get Involved Section -->
<section id="involved" class="py-16">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-12">Get Involved</h2>

    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <p class="text-lg mb-8">
        KRF is in its first chapter and this is when every voice, skill, and idea matters the most. While our formal projects are in development, there are already ways for individuals, institutions, and communities to connect with us:
      </p>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-12">
        <div class="bg-primary-50 p-6 rounded-lg">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3 text-primary-600">Collaborate on Research</h3>
          <p>Partner with us on studies, field surveys, and policy recommendations.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-primary-50 p-6 rounded-lg">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3 text-primary-600">Volunteer Your Skills</h3>
          <p>From field outreach to design, data analysis to community facilitation — your expertise can help shape impactful work.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-primary-50 p-6 rounded-lg">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3 text-primary-600">Host Conversations</h3>
          <p>Co-create dialogues, workshops, and knowledge-sharing sessions with us.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-primary-50 p-6 rounded-lg">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3 text-primary-600">Stay Updated</h3>
          <p>Join our mailing list to hear about upcoming projects, events, and opportunities to contribute.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <p class="text-lg text-center">
        Whether you are an individual with a vision, an organisation with aligned goals, or a community group with on-the-ground insights, we want to hear from you.
      </p>

      <div class="mt-12 text-center">
        <a href="mailto:info@krf.org" class="inline-block bg-primary-800 text-white font-bold py-3 px-6 rounded-lg hover:bg-primary-600 transition-colors">
          Contact Us
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
